  <div class="column_holder">
    <h1>
      <img alt="JOBS" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=JOBS" />
    </h1>
    <div class="column_heading">
      <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTop"><p>GRIN is constantly looking for talented people. All available positions are listed below. Apply via the form or by e-mail.  If you are interested in a position that isn&rsquo;t listed, please send your CV via e-mail to jobs@grin.se.</p></span></div>
    <div class="column_sep">
      <img src="img/jobs/jobs_open_sep.png" alt="Open positions" /></div>
    
    
      <div class="column_content">
        <h1>
          <img alt="Friday 04 July 2008" src="/images/headers/pf_small/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Friday 04 July 2008" />
        </h1>
        <h2>
          <img alt="Special Effects Artist" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Special Effects Artist" />
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p>&nbsp;<font face="Calibri"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black">RESPONSIBILITIES</span></strong></font></p>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Work closely with effects programmers. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Create all aspects of 2D and 3D game effects. This includes particlesystems, animating textures, polygonal effects meshes, and assets that may be used procedurally by programmers. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">May contribute to design and/or conceptualization efforts as needed. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Create polygonal and texture effects assets to be used by programmers. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Work closely with programmers to ensure visual quality of procedural effects. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Using 3D software, simulate and render animations of in-game effects as proof-of-concept for current and future hardware. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Create realistic effects such as fire, smoke, and explosions using limited game resources.</font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Meet project deadlines/milestones as set by project leads. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Actively participate in team/department meetings. </font></span></div>
<div style="background: white; line-height: normal"><font face="Calibri"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black">EXPECTATIONS<br />
<br />
</span></strong></font></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Ability to model and texture in 3D. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Experience with particle effects. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Minimum of two years of applicable industry experience. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Strong technical aptitude related to 3D modeling tools and game engine technologies.</font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Fluent knowledge of Maya, Max and Photoshop. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Graphic design or fine art skills a plus.</font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Experience with programming or scripting languages a plus. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Experience with motion picture quality rendered effects a plus. </font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings">&sect;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%"><font face="Calibri">Ability to be receptive to art direction and to perform well within a collaborative team environment. </font></span></div>
<div style="background: white; line-height: normal"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black"><font face="Calibri">DEMO REEL REQUIREMENTS</font></span></strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black"><br />
<font face="Calibri">Samples that demonstrate 3D effects work (online, CD or DVD format) - muzzle flashes, explosions, smoke, fire etc. Applicants must provide demo reel/CD/DVD or website address to be considered for any artist position <br />
<br />
</font></span><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black"><font face="Calibri">Positions in Gothenburg.<br />
<br />
</font></span></strong></div>
<div style="background: white; line-height: normal"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black"><font face="Calibri">The last date for applying for this position is September 30, but the opening will be filled as soon as possible.</font></span></strong></div></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column_nav">
        <span class="column_nav_cat">Contact</span>
        <p>
          Please send your application through the online form below, or by regular mail to
          our physical adress. If you prefer to send your application by email click
          <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#97;&#114;&#116;&#64;&#103;&#114;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#115;&#101;">here</a>.</p>
